SAIDO LABS ADDITIONS
================================================================================

The following modules were created by Saido Labs LLC and are NOT derived from
nano-claude-code:

  - Knowledge engine (saido_agent/knowledge/) — ingest, compile, query,
    grounding, linting, indexing, structural analysis, synthetic data,
    fine-tuning, report generation
  - SmartRAG bridge (saido_agent/knowledge/bridge.py)
  - Model routing engine (saido_agent/core/routing.py, cost_tracker.py)
  - Security hardening (saido_agent/core/permissions.py, ssrf.py)
  - Voice SDK (saido_agent/voice/) — STT, VAD, TTS, pipeline
  - REST API (saido_agent/api/) — server, routes, auth, RBAC, billing,
    enterprise features, WebSocket
  - Plugin marketplace (saido_agent/plugins/marketplace.py)
  - React web UI (frontend/)
  - All test files (tests/)
  - Deployment infrastructure (Dockerfile, docker-compose, CI/CD, migrations)

